Why Check mid % 2 Instead of nums[mid] % 2?
Wrong
if(nums[mid] % 2 == 1)

This checks whether the value is odd.

The algorithm does not depend on values.

Correct
if(mid % 2 == 1)

This checks whether the index is odd.

The pair structure depends on indexes, not values.

